Complete the following items before class for the Labs:


Option 1 (not recommended on Mac M-series):
    1. Create a GitHub (https://github.com/) account (if you donâ€™t already have one)
    2. Download and build the container image from https://github.com/redhat-ai-services/etx-delivery-labs

Option 2:
    1. Download and install Node (https://nodejs.org/en/download) & NPM
    2. Download and install Python 3.11 (https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-31112/)
    3. Download and install Podman Desktop (https://podman-desktop.io/downloads) with AI Lab extension (https://podman-desktop.io/docs/ai-lab/installing)
    4. Verify you can run Docling with
        podman run -p 5001:5001 -e DOCLING_SERVE_ENABLE_UI=true quay.io/docling-project/docling-serve
        Download and install Ollama
    5. Pull Ollama Images (https://ollama.com/download) using:
        ollama pull llama2
        ollama pull granite3.2:2b
